public class Action
extends EnumProperty

Defines the type of action to invoke when an alarm is triggered.

Examples: 

 //creating a new property
 Action action = Action.audio();
 
 if (action.isAudio()) {
        //it's an "AUDIO" alarm
 }

Michael Angstadt
